\u00f3w, gdzie widzowie mog\u0105 zobaczy\u0107 efekty na sk\u00f3rze.<\/li>\n<li><b>Warto\u015bciowe tre\u015bci:<\/b> Podziel si\u0119 wskaz\u00f3wkami i poradami zwi\u0105zanymi z produktem, kt\u00f3re mog\u0105 zainteresowa\u0107 Twoj\u0105 grup\u0119 docelow\u0105. Na przyk\u0142ad, je\u015bli reklamujesz kosmetyki, mo\u017cesz zaprezentowa\u0107 tutorial makija\u017cowy.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, kluczem do sukcesu w reklamach wideo na Amazonie jest dostosowanie tre\u015bci do wymog\u00f3w platformy oraz tworzenie anga\u017cuj\u0105cych i informacyjnych film\u00f3w. Pami\u0119taj, aby Twoje wideo by\u0142o wizualn\u0105 opowie\u015bci\u0105, kt\u00f3ra przyci\u0105gnie uwag\u0119 klient\u00f3w. <\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak Tworzy\u0107 Skuteczne Wideo Reklamowe na Amazonie?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak przyci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4201,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[3],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4200","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kampanieppc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4200"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4200"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4200\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4201"}],"wp:attachment":